reviews.text: Appreciated the janitors and staff here, they have passion of the job and take initiative to cleanup the tables for customers, also they saw my girl need a high chair, he went to search one for my kid. Another staff is a waitress (she wears formal suit), she hold the door open for my baby stroller, she is really helpful.

Went there on Sunday 5th of May around 5 PM... the staff were all busy chatting and having a blast while not caring or giving a damn about what their customers want. I opted for a Fillet o Fish burger without a cheese and yes I got the cheese. They failed to even provide tissues, not that I didn't have them but they were just so distracted. Not the cleaning staff but the serving ones. My last time visiting here. I was in a hurry and wanted a quick snack, bad move have learnt!
Another mc donald , whatelse
